reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Important that it hangs in the right direction!
reviews.reviewText: At first, I was really upset when I got this package because it looked like all the car fresheners were incorrectly printed, so that it said "saw I that" on all sides. It wasn't until I flipped them around that I saw it's just reverse printed like a mirror image... So, as long as you hang them the right direction and they don't start swinging all over the place then the funny message will be visible! So for that reason, it's a little disappointing. As for the scent, I didn't smell much of a scent. I think the main purpose here is for a gag gift. Overall, its cute and it was cheap. these will make for a funny stocking stuffer!
